{"tid":1416274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好俾位777入，唔好俾位共產黨入，唔好激嬲共產黨","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:58.000Z","uid":281311,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe04c4632014848cd068823b70105489db772800","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"一個口號，冇鼓吹暴力，冇殺人放火，你咁都要自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n你成日承認對方思維咁反咩對啫？觀感嘅嘢，你自己都心虛點說服人？以前衝擊都嫌暴力架啦！<br />\n<br />\n如果泛民驚dq所以唔想講咁咪唔好講囉，係咪怕出去時唔跟群眾叫口號會監尬？但唔使跟777口徑叫人唔好講架嘛<br />\n<br />\n早幾日班5毛帶風向話個口號唔好，連登會知係5毛帶風向，777講完劉細良講下，就自己幫埋5毛帶風向<br />\n<br />\n唔使驚，唔使心虛，唔自製白色恐怖，唔自我審查<br />\n<br />\n大聲講，自豪咁講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef3e59f7ce4fb40e7c76c5518cdee1f62427c700","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c3befee8d9aca7d412332eec296d2e9aab7ab3f","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ad3e93d60b6ea5dc1347a5ad3a350461953fda9","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"774694b0a80ad627f065e1b7d505997935a18f36","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"60227fba9f49ae861130e2e62d566022fa8bbdca","tid":1416274,"uid":281311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><